    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Minimally invasive stone cleaning treatments for historic masonry in sculpture and architecture that aim to avoid damage to surface topography of material while mechanically removing the soiling agent or coating.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
